@startuml
title Production Planning

actor ProductionManager
participant ManagementSystem
participant Warehouse
participant ProductionLine

ProductionManager -> ManagementSystem : Select product

ManagementSystem -> Warehouse : Check raw materials
Warehouse --> ManagementSystem : Materials available

ManagementSystem -> ProductionLine : Assign production job
ProductionLine --> ManagementSystem : Production started

ManagementSystem --> ProductionManager : Production plan saved

@enduml
